**Core tenets**

- Understanding the user goals w.r.t to the product
- What is the business goals?
- **Onboarding** :
    - How did it come to your attention? Why are you trying it now?
    - What is the one line summary of this app at this stage?
    - What is the buzz so far? Is it popular, etc?
    
    <aside>
    ðŸ’¡ What is the appâ€™s value proposition and marketing? What is the product team trying to convey?
    
    </aside>
    
    - What is the experience of getting started?
    - How does the app explains itself in the first minute? â†’ Clear what it did, friendly, easy to comprehend or confusing, etc?
    - How did you feel while exploring the app? â†’ Funny, interesting content, etc
    - Did the app deliver on your expectation?
    - How long did you spend using the app?
    
    â€”-
    
- **Do you continue to use the app?**
    - How often do you use the app?
    - When you tend to you use it? What compels you to use it?
    - What do you other people think of this app? â†’ Read reviews, comments, about it

**Future**

- Based on your understanding, how success will be the app?
- What it should do to be successful?

